{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"DeviceMotionEvent.DeviceMotionEvent()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/DeviceMotionEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Device_orientation_events\">Device orientation events <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>构造函数</summary><ol><li><em><code>DeviceMotionEvent()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration\"><code>acceleration</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/accelerationIncludingGravity\"><code>accelerationIncludingGravity</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/interval\"><code>interval</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/rotationRate\"><code>rotationRate</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Device Orientation Events 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEventAcceleration\"><code>DeviceMotionEventAcceleration</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEventRotationRate\"><code>DeviceMotionEventRotationRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceOrientationEvent\"><code>DeviceOrientationEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>非标准:</strong> 该特性是非标准的，请尽量不要在生产环境中使用它！</p></div>\n<p>The <strong><code>DeviceMotionEvent</code></strong> constructor 会创建一个新的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">var deviceMotionEvent = new DeviceMotionEvent(type[, options])\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"type\"><code>type</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>必须是 <code>\"devicemotion\"</code>.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"options\"><code>options</code><span class=\"badge inline optional\">可选</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>可选项如下：</p>\n    <ul>\n      <li><code>acceleration</code>: 一个对象，包含设备在 X，Y 和 Z 三个轴线上的加速度。加速度的单位为<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meter_per_second_squared\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">m/s2</a>.</li>\n      <li><code>accelerationIncludingGravity</code>: 一个对象，包含设备在 X，Y 和 Z 三个轴线上，重力作用下的加速度。加速度的单位为<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meter_per_second_squared\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">m/s2</a>.</li>\n      <li><code>rotationRate</code>: 一个对象，包含设备的定向在三个定向轴 alpha, beta 和 gamma 上的偏移比率。偏移比率的单位是每秒偏移的角度。</li>\n      <li><code>interval</code>: 时间间隔，单位毫秒，表示设备获取数据的间隔时间。</li>\n    </ul>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"说明","title":"说明","isH3":false,"content":"<p>无特别说明。</p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容","id":"浏览器兼容","isH3":false,"query":"api.DeviceMotionEvent.DeviceMotionEvent","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/DeviceMotionEvent/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"说明","id":"说明"},{"text":"浏览器兼容","id":"浏览器兼容"}],"summary":"The DeviceMotionEvent constructor 会创建一个新的 DeviceMotionEvent.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"DeviceM